title: 831 49 "The Broken Couple! Sanji and Pudding Enter!"Transliteration: "Kamen Fūfu Sanji ♡ Purin Nyūjō!" (Japanese:仮面夫婦　サンジ♡プリン入場！) Yusuke Suzuki Kisa Miura April 8, 2018(2018-04-08)
transformers_text: 831 49 The Broken Couple Sanji and Pudding Enter Transliteration Kamen F fu Sanji Pur in Ny j Japanese Yusuke Suzuki Kisa Miura April 8 2018 2018 04 08 As the Tea Party begins the Fire Tank Pirates and Caesar Clown make preparations to commit their assassination attempt on Big Mom Inside the venue Big Mom receives the portrait of Mother Carmel as well as presents from her guests and she reveals that she will be opening the Ta mate Box after the wedding Meanwhile Sanji struggles to not be fooled by Pudding's facade as the two of them practise their vows before being flown out to the venue
